---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import ProfileImage from "../assets/halim.png";
---

<header>
  <div class="container">
    <Image
      src={ProfileImage}
      alt="Md. Halim (Bhola ji)"
      class="profile-image"
    />
    <div class="header-text">
      <h1>Md. Halim (Bhola ji)</h1>
      <p>District General Secretary, Darbhanga (JDU)</p>
      <p>Over 35 years of dedicated public service</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<section id="introduction">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Introduction</h2>
    <p>
      Md. Halim (Bhola ji) is a respected leader with over 35 years of
      experience...
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="professional-journey">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Professional Journey</h2>
    <div class="journey-item">
      <h3>RJD (20 Years)</h3>
      <p>
        Md. Halim dedicated two decades to the Rashtriya Janata Dal (RJD)...
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="journey-item">
      <h3>JDU (15 Years)</h3>
      <p>
        For the past 15 years, he has been a key figure in the Janata Dal
        (United) [JDU]...
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="community-service">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Community Service</h2>
    <div class="service-item">
      <h3>Covid-19 Relief Efforts</h3>
      <p>
        During the challenging times of Covid-19, Md. Halim led initiatives...
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-item">
      <h3>Winter Relief Programs</h3>
      <p>
        Understanding the harshness of winter, he organized the distribution of
        blankets...
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="vision-goals">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Vision and Goals</h2>
    <p>Md. Halim envisions a prosperous and inclusive Darbhanga...</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="contact">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Feel free to reach out for any community-related concerns or to
      collaborate...
    </p>
    <p>
      Email: <a href="mailto:example@example.com">example@example.com</a>
    </p>
    <p>Phone: <a href="tel:+911234567890">+91 12345 67890</a></p>
  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <div class="container">
    <p>&copy; 2024 Md. Halim (Bhola ji). All Rights Reserved.</p>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    color: #333;
  }

  .container {
    width: 90%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  header {
    background-color: #0056b3;
    color: white;
    padding: 60px 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .profile-image {
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .header-text {
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 2.5em;
  }

  h2 {
    color: #0056b3;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  p {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  section {
    padding: 40px 0;
  }

  .journey-item,
  .service-item {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  footer {
    background-color: #333;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px 0;
    font-size: 0.9em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2em;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.5em;
    }

    .container {
      padding: 10px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 1.8em;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.2em;
    }

    header {
      padding: 40px 0;
    }

    section {
      padding: 20px 0;
    }

    footer {
      font-size: 0.8em;
    }
  }
</style>
